{"id":17955,"date":"2022-12-31T04:21:07","date_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:21:07","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/nd.wv3.net\/amg-car\/thi-truong-o-to-viet-tang-truong-nhanh-nhat-dong-nam-a.html"},"modified":"2022-12-31T04:21:07","modified_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:21:07","slug":"thi-truong-o-to-viet-tang-truong-nhanh-nhat-dong-nam-a","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/2022\/12\/31\/thi-truong-o-to-viet-tang-truong-nhanh-nhat-dong-nam-a\/","title":{"rendered":"Th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u00f4 t\u00f4 Vi\u1ec7t t\u0103ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng nhanh nh\u1ea5t \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1"},"content":{"rendered":"<\/p>\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\n<p>Doanh s\u1ed1 322.963 xe sau 10 th\u00e1ng 2022 c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ee9c t\u0103ng 52,2%, cao nh\u1ea5t khu v\u1ef1c, theo AAF (Hi\u1ec7p h\u1ed9i \u00f4t\u00f4 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1).<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">M\u1ee9c ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 322.963 xe c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a Hi\u1ec7p h\u1ed9i c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t \u00f4 t\u00f4 Vi\u1ec7t Nam (VAMA), bao g\u1ed3m doanh s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u00e3ng thu\u1ed9c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c n\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u kh\u00e1c.  \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, kh\u00f4ng bao g\u1ed3m VinFast v\u00e0 TC Motor, \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i xe Hyundai.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea doanh s\u1ed1 b\u00e1n xe m\u1edbi v\u00e0 t\u0103ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng so v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng k\u1ef3 n\u0103m 2021 (sau 10 th\u00e1ng n\u0103m 2022):<\/p>\n<table style=\"\" cellspacing=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">Th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">B\u00e1n h\u00e0ng (xe)<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">S\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n (%)<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">Indonesia<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">851.413<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">21.1<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">n\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u00e1i Lan<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">750.597<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">25.9<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">Malaysia<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">577.902<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">50,7<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">Vi\u1ec7t Nam<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">322.963<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">52.2<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">philippines<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">280.300<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">30.9<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">Singapore<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">35.678<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">-30.1<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">Myanma<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">6.730<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">-14,5<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p class=\"Normal\">S\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a AAF bao g\u1ed3m 7 th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1: Indonesia, Th\u00e1i Lan, Malaysia, Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Philippines, Singapore v\u00e0 Myanmar.  C\u00e1c qu\u1ed1c gia nh\u01b0 L\u00e0o, Timor Lester v\u00e0 Brunei kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 d\u1eef li\u1ec7u.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Sau 10 th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2022, Indonesia v\u1eabn l\u00e0 th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 \u00f4 t\u00f4 m\u1edbi l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t, h\u01a1n 850.000 xe.  Theo sau l\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 Malaysia.  Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 4 v\u1ec1 ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 \u00f4 t\u00f4 m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u0103ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng mua s\u1eafm cao nh\u1ea5t, 52,2% so v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng k\u1ef3 n\u0103m 2021.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"Nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng tham kh\u1ea3o xe t\u1ea1i tri\u1ec3n l\u00e3m VMS 2022.  \u1ea2nh: Ph\u1ea1m Trung\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/thi-truong-o-to-viet-tang-truong-nhanh-nhat-dong.jpg\" title=\"thi-truong-o-to-viet-tang-truong-nhanh-nhat-dong\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/thi-truong-o-to-viet-tang-truong-nhanh-nhat-dong-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/thi-truong-o-to-viet-tang-truong-nhanh-nhat-dong-600x360.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/thi-truong-o-to-viet-tang-truong-nhanh-nhat-dong.jpg 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">Nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng tham kh\u1ea3o xe t\u1ea1i tri\u1ec3n l\u00e3m VMS 2022.  \u1ea2nh: Ph\u1ea1m Trung<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">V\u1edbi d\u00e2n s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng th\u1ee9 3 khu v\u1ef1c (sau Indonesia v\u00e0 Philippines) nh\u01b0ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 \u00f4 t\u00f4 t\u0103ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng cao nh\u1ea5t, Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m t\u1edbi.  Theo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a VAMA, t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 10, doanh s\u1ed1 b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea1t g\u1ea7n 333.000 xe.  N\u1ebfu duy tr\u00ec m\u1ee9c t\u0103ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u01b0 hai th\u00e1ng v\u1eeba qua, doanh s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 8 n\u0103m, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2014, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1ed1c 400.000 xe.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Singapore v\u00e0 Myanmar l\u00e0 hai th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 doanh s\u1ed1 t\u0103ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u00e2m.  Trong khi Malaysia, th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 xe m\u1edbi l\u1edbn th\u1ee9 ba trong khu v\u1ef1c, c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u0103ng doanh s\u1ed1 ch\u1ec9 sau Vi\u1ec7t Nam, 50,7%.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">L\u01b0\u1ee3ng ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 \u00f4 t\u00f4 m\u1edbi sau 10 th\u00e1ng n\u0103m 2022 c\u1ee7a 7 th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 n\u00f3i tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea1t h\u01a1n 2,8 tri\u1ec7u chi\u1ebfc, t\u0103ng 34,7% so v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng k\u1ef3 n\u0103m 2021.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align:right;\">Thanh Nh\u00e0n <\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right\"><strong>AMGCAR.VN<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/p><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Doanh s\u1ed1 322.963 xe sau 10 th\u00e1ng 2022 c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ee9c t\u0103ng 52,2%, cao nh\u1ea5t khu v\u1ef1c, theo AAF (Hi\u1ec7p h\u1ed9i \u00f4t\u00f4 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1). M\u1ee9c ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 322.963 xe c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a Hi\u1ec7p h\u1ed9i c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t \u00f4 t\u00f4 Vi\u1ec7t Nam (VAMA), bao g\u1ed3m doanh s\u1ed1 [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":16375,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[75],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17955"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=17955"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17955\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/16375"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=17955"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=17955"},{"taxonomy":"p